            "text": "{\n  \"id\": \"resp_04e8376915c3719a0069d7a881acb48196a08105a209ebbd7b\",\n  \"object\": \"response\",\n  \"created_at\": 1775741057,\n  \"status\": \"completed\",\n  \"background\": false,\n  \"billing\": {\n    \"payer\": \"openai\"\n  },\n  \"completed_at\": 1775741062,\n  \"error\": null,\n  \"frequency_penalty\": 0.0,\n  \"incomplete_details\": null,\n  \"instructions\": null,\n  \"max_output_tokens\": 500,\n  \"max_tool_calls\": null,\n  \"model\": \"o4-mini-2025-04-16\",\n  \"output\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"rs_04e8376915c3719a0069d7a8828cf88196bf05f3f290f52933\",\n      \"type\": \"reasoning\",\n      \"summary\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"summary_text\",\n          \"text\": \"**Counting letters in strawberry**\\n\\nOkay, the question is about counting the \\\"r's\\\" in the word \\\"strawberry.\\\" When I spell it out, I see the letters: s, t, r, a, w, b, e, r, r, y. I notice that there are three \\\"r's\\\" located at positions 3, 8, and 9. So, the answer is clearly 3. I might wonder about lower-case, but it seems straightforward. Thus, I'll respond that there are 3 \\\"r's\\\" in \\\"strawberry.\\\"\"\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"msg_04e8376915c3719a0069d7a8867c20819686f0198dee0e5ead\",\n      \"type\": \"message\",\n      \"status\": \"completed\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"output_text\",\n          \"annotations\": [],\n          \"logprobs\": [],\n          \"text\": \"There are three \\u201cr\\u201ds in the word \\u201cstrawberry.\\u201d\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"role\": \"assistant\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"parallel_tool_calls\": true,\n  \"presence_penalty\": 0.0,\n  \"previous_response_id\": null,\n  \"prompt_cache_key\": null,\n  \"prompt_cache_retention\": null,\n  \"reasoning\": {\n    \"effort\": \"low\",\n    \"summary\": \"detailed\"\n  },\n  \"safety_identifier\": null,\n  \"service_tier\": \"default\",\n  \"store\": true,\n  \"temperature\": 1.0,\n  \"text\": {\n    \"format\": {\n      \"type\": \"text\"\n    },\n    \"verbosity\": \"medium\"\n  },\n  \"tool_choice\": \"auto\",\n  \"tools\": [],\n  \"top_logprobs\": 0,\n  \"top_p\": 1.0,\n  \"truncation\": \"disabled\",\n  \"usage\": {\n    \"input_tokens\": 16,\n    \"input_tokens_details\": {\n      \"cached_tokens\": 0\n    },\n    \"output_tokens\": 170,\n    \"output_tokens_details\": {\n      \"reasoning_tokens\": 128\n    },\n    \"total_tokens\": 186\n  },\n  \"user\": null,\n  \"metadata\": {}\n}"
